Your best protection from #COVID19 will be a combination of the following:

✔️Getting a COVID-19 #vaccine
✔️Wearing a mask (correctly)😷
✔️Staying at least 6 feet away from others↔️
✔️Avoiding crowds❌
✔️Washing your hands often🧼

No one tool alone is going to stop the pandemic! https://t.co/skno9Mfqsc
